data.description: IMPORTANT PRICE REDUCTION. MOTIVATED SELLERS.  Welcome to an ideal 3-bed, 2-bath haven, looking like a doll house with 2-car garage, 1,200 sq.ft. Meticulously designed modern elegance meets functionality for family dreams. The heart of the home is the open kitchen. Contemporary layout fosters open living, harmonizing luxury and comfort. Features include crown molding, 24x24 porcelain tiles, tray ceilings, granite counters, wood cabinets. Retreat to master suite with dual sinks, spacious shower, his-and-her closets. to many details to call this sweet home. Shingle roof, asphalt driveway, gutters adorn exterior. A complete package of style, comfort, community. Don't miss this opportunity to experience Golden Gate Estates living.
